    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic, a dedicated hobbyist, or as a source for parts. The engine currently suffers from a severe oil leak and overheating issues, likely indicating a failing head gasket, while the transmission exhibits significant hesitation and slipping between gears. Externally, the body shows several large dents, noticeable rust on the wheel wells, and the clear coat is peeling extensively on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components, including the radio and rear power windows, are non-functional. This car will require a trailer for transport as it is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
